org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_prices ON spree_prices.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.variant_id = spree_variants.id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.currency = 'EUR' AND spree_prices.amount IS NOT NULL AND spree_variants.id = "$1" LIMIT "$2"
